PAL is an independent execution-oriented binary reconstruction and
forensic analysis research project.

PAL uses the public APIs of Ghidra and PyGhidra.
Ghidra and PyGhidra are separate projects maintained by the National
Security Agency Research Directorate and licensed under Apache-2.0.

PAL is not affiliated with or endorsed by the National Security Agency.
